### SQL UPDATE Query for Offline Data Modification

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/why-nosql.html

This SQL statement demonstrates updating multiple rows in a database based on a condition. It is used to illustrate potential data inconsistencies in offline-first applications if not handled carefully during replication.

```sql
UPDATE docs
SET docs.color = 'red'
WHERE docs.color = 'blue';
```

