### SQL Query for Relational Data Retrieval

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/why-nosql.html

This SQL query shows how to retrieve data from two related tables ('city' and 'customer') by joining them based on a common field ('city_id'). It is presented as a comparison to NoSQL data retrieval methods.

```sql
SELECT *
FROM city
WHERE city.name = 'Tokyo'
LEFT JOIN customer ON customer.city_id = city.id;
```

