### SQL UPDATE Query for Inventory Management

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/why-nosql.html

This SQL statement illustrates updating inventory status based on stock levels. It is used to explain potential replication conflicts in distributed systems when concurrent updates occur on the same data.

```sql
# mark all items out of stock as inStock=FALSE
UPDATE  Table_A
SET  Table_A.inStock = FALSE
FROM  Table_A
WHER  Table_A.amountInStock = 0;
```

