### Querying for Incomplete Tasks in RxDB

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/articles/ionic-database.html

This RxDB snippet demonstrates how to query for documents where the 'done' field is false. It uses the 'find' method with a selector and then executes the query to retrieve the matching documents. This is useful for filtering tasks that are not yet completed.

```javascript
const foundDocuments = await myDatabase.todos.find({
    selector: {
        done: {
            $eq: false
        }
    }
}).exec();
```
